{"tid":241531,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"錢人船P, 窮撚勿入。","createTime":"2017-05-13T08:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T09:59:18.000Z","uid":17232,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87976ecebbddf6e5b1aac423462973c1ca4eb92e","tid":241531,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出太空。 <br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻Hyperion，<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/162418_72648051e2bca4df074139c055cce5fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F162418_72648051e2bca4df074139c055cce5fe.jpg&h=f08cf211&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/162418_09d604226269a3cf09a6472b487679b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F162418_09d604226269a3cf09a6472b487679b5.jpg&h=90936efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/163014_c15487b4d20fbbe67bdb343ce863e790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F163014_c15487b4d20fbbe67bdb343ce863e790.jpg&h=9db71a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 Roger Young坐20人 太空飛船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u920uLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu920uLa.jpg&h=5f61735a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/162943_511801b2b27108b775edbcc38865cbe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F162943_511801b2b27108b775edbcc38865cbe5.jpg&h=9423211f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82tgPxu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82tgPxu.jpg&h=e268f77f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4un3k3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4un3k3.jpg&h=0e9acef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。 <br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒。 <br />\n<br />\n星期五 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$400000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起40萬去船河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"3689c22cb4c07089ab99ca4444dfb9ee7e0cedeb","tid":241531,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"標題打漏，係有錢人船p"},{"pid":"bcc237fc398019f786512ff8768a4946148031f8","tid":241531,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"一個笑話講得多都唔好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba00060c62f2d7a76583b52dd4ede12afdb7842","tid":241531,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"你個三部機舊成咁 真係冇咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01cb6b6dc14ccf43b1cea9ef78a77c7b1288971","tid":241531,"uid":103542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"冇錢，負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e925a4020d72433bbf7bae93e92de0ad73a29b2e","tid":241531,"uid":18653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"請問過數入邊個戶口？錢已備<br />\nBtw 有冇暈浪藥提供，搭親太空船都會暈，短程上轉月球都嘔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24806e26265fd3bd412e22bf0e6d7ac80b5c846f","tid":241531,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"仲用緊呢幾隻船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bb399e91eaf64b1ca6093bfb0ce7c709ff